<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom=
:6.6pt;
margin-left:-.15pt'>Welcome to the Fashion Connect API. This document provi=
des
a detailed overview of all the available API endpoints, their functionaliti=
es,
request formats, and response structures.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom=
:15.55pt;
margin-left:-.15pt'>The API is a RESTful service built with Node.js, Expres=
s,
and MongoDB. It powers a fashion e-commerce platform connecting clients with
designers.</p>

<h2 style=3D'margin-left:-.15pt'>Base URL</h2>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:166.9pt;margin-bo=
ttom:
.75pt;margin-left:-.15pt;line-height:225%'>All API endpoints are prefixed w=
ith
the following base URL: <span style=3D'font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-fon=
t-family:
Consolas;mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas;background:#F6F8FA'>http://localhost=
:8000/api/v1
</span><span style=3D'font-size:9.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height=
:225%;
color:#2B2B2B'>Authentication</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom=
:6.55pt;
margin-left:-.15pt'>Authentication is handled using JSON Web Tokens (JWT).<=
/p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-left:24.6pt'>After a successful login,=
 an <span
class=3DSpellE><span style=3D'font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:=
Consolas;
mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas'>accessToken</span></span> and <span
class=3DSpellE><span style=3D'font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:=
Consolas;
mso-bidi-font-family:Consolas'>refreshToken</span></span> are generated.</p>

